    public class HtmlParserFormTable
extends java.util.HashMap
    Contains a table of all forms of a parsed HTML response. Specific forms are directly accessible by their form index or their form name.
    See Also:
    HtmlContentParser.getFormTable(), HtmlParserForm, Serialized Form
